		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hello all,
<br />
<br />Can anybody help me with my project? My project is to take SM1 for FDS and make it match SMB2J in Graphics, and Physics, and Gameplay. I already imported all the graphics using yy-chr, and impoved player jump physics, using WindHex, but I need help with two things:
<br />
<br /> 
<br />
<br />1. Insert skid sound from SMB2J, when Mario/Luigi make a sharp turn.
<br />
<br /> 
<br />
<br />2. Make the timer routine count down in every X-4 stage.
<br />
<br /> 
<br />
<br />I have the .asm files for both SMB1J and SMB2J in my computer, its just that I don't know assembly, and the computer technecians that I know do not know 6502 assembly. If anybody here knows 6502 assembly and would like to help me this would be great. I can post a patch of my rom if anybody can help. And as I said, just the skid sound, and timer routine for Castle Stages needed to finish my hack. Thanks.  <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

		</td>
